 Veteran Nollywood actor, Kayode Odumosu, popularly known as Pa Kasumu, is dead. He died on Sunday afternoon after a protracted illness. Pa Kasumu's death was announced by actress, Foluke Daramola-Salako, on her Instagram page. She said, “Our model veteran actor, Pa Kasumu Kayode Odumosu, finally takes a bow. "It is with heavy pain in our hearts that we regret to announce that our #paraafricafoundation model actor, Pa Kasumu, has given up the ghost after a brief illness. “The news was broken by a close source that stays around the hospital he gave up the ghost. "We will keep you updated with further information on this.”